This place looks nice from the street but when you walk in it is much larger and beautiful. The service was excellent and the food superb. Food:Iberico ham and manchego: amazingJamon croquette: deliciousToasted bread with tomato: simple and greatCatalonian sausage with beans: amazingDrink: rose champagne and then amazing sangria with fresh berries. I will go back for another meal with in town. I would highly recommend.
